Company: California Department of Child Support Services
Description of incident: The California Department of Child Support Services has notified individuals of a data breach that resulted in unauthorized disclosure of personal information. On April 7, 2014 letters from the Solano County Department of Child Support Services were misplaced while in the custody of a contracted courier who was transporting mail to the US Post Office. Those affected are asked to call the Department of Child Support Services at 1-866-901-3212.
